name: Weird Angles
tag_list: bollywood, india, movies, reviews, aggregator, cinema, kannada
overview: Weird Angles is an Indian Movie Review Aggregator.It currently Aggregates reviews of Hindi and Kannada language movies. It collects reviews of all the critics from newspapers,TV channels,blogs/websites and video reviews on youtube;and presents an aggregate score. It also provides complete cast details,release dates,trailers,plot synopsis,movie screenshots,wallpapers,pictures of promotional events and imdb rating for the benifit of users. Movies releasing Next Week And Movies In Theaters are also listed.
